text: Iva Tepeshanova (; born February 19, 1983 in Sofia) is a Bulgarian rhythmic gymnast. Tepeshanova competed for Bulgaria in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. There she was 15th in the qualification round and did not advance to the final of 10 competitors. == References == == External links == * Iva Tepeshanova at Sports-Reference.com Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Sportspeople from Sofia
